#Download

#Where was the coldest temperature readings?

# Remove rows with missing temperature values
met_no_na <- met[!is.na(met$temp), ]

# Find the location(s) of the coldest temperature close to -17.2C
coldest_temp <- met_no_na[abs(met_no_na$temp - (-17.2)) < 0.01, ]

# Display the relevant columns (latitude, longitude, temperature, and elevation)
coldest_temp_locations <- coldest_temp[, c("lat", "lon", "temp", "elev")]
print(coldest_temp_locations)
